      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Well-kept older car in good overall condition and a solid driver-quality example. It presents nicely with typical light age-related cosmetic wear, but nothing suggesting a project or rough car. The interior, body, and overall appearance show it has been cared for, and buyers should expect a usable, presentable vehicle that is ready to enjoy while still not being a mint/show-level example. A good fit for someone wanting a clean classic/older vehicle without paying top-tier money.",
