      "description": "Solid fair-condition driver that appears complete and usable, but not fully sorted. It presents respectably from a distance, with visible age, cosmetic blemishes, and wear to the paint, trim, and interior consistent with a car that has been used and not fully restored. Expect an honest car that can be enjoyed as-is with room for improvement, and plan on some ongoing mechanical, cosmetic, and general sorting depending on how nice you want it to be.",
